## Domain model (conceptual)

```
Account
  ├── id, name, type (bank | broker | cash)
  ├── provider (KBC, Saxo, DEGIRO, …)
  ├── totalValue, currency
  └── holdings[]

Holding
  ├── asset name / identifier (ISIN, ticker — TBD in schema)
  ├── quantity, value, currency
  └── assetClass (equities | bonds | cash | … — TBD enum)

Allocation (computed)
  └── assetClass → % of total across all accessible accounts
```

Exact columns TBD in first migration. Regenerate `lib/supabase/types.ts` after schema lands.

