## User access (v0.1)

- **Many users → one account** (see glossary)
- v0.1: store allowed `account_ids` (or equivalent) in Supabase Auth **`app_metadata`**
- Repository must filter accounts/holdings to those the current user may access
- RLS on tables must enforce the same rules — do not rely on UI filtering alone
- Post–v0.1: proper join table + permissions (see roadmap)

