## Folder structure

Follow `.cursor/project/architecture.mdc`:

```
lib/accounts/
  domain/
    accountModels.ts
    accountService.ts
  data/
    accountSchemas.ts      # Zod + DTOs (DB/API shapes)
    accountRepository.ts   # Supabase queries; validate responses
  presentation/
    accountPresentationModels.ts
    accountPresentationMapper.ts   # Strip UUIDs, provider IDs, tokens
  ui/
    useAccountsViewModel.ts          # List page (client, if needed)
    createAccountDetailViewModel.ts  # Detail (server, if needed)
    AccountList.tsx
    AccountDetail.tsx
    …
```

Sync job stub (future provider pull) — prefer `data/accountSyncJob.ts` or `data/providers/` subfolder; not in `ui/`.

---

## Data flow

```
accountRepository (validate with accountSchemas)
  → map DTO → domain models
  → accountService (filter by user access from app_metadata)
  → accountPresentationMapper (remove sensitive fields)
  → ViewModel
  → Components
```

**Repository** is the only layer that queries Supabase for account data.

