## Provider integrations (phased)

| Phase | Approach |
|-------|----------|
| **v0.1** | Seed/manual data in Supabase; sync job **stub** (structure only, no live KBC/Saxo/DEGIRO calls required for first UI) |
| **Later** | Incremental API integrations per provider; never expose provider tokens to client |

Provider external IDs stored in DB but **not** passed to UI (presentation layer).

