## Security

- RLS on `accounts`, `holdings`, and any join/access tables
- Presentation mapper required for all UI-bound account data
- Never return `sync_tokens`, provider credentials, or raw provider payloads to ViewModels/components
- Provider sync runs server-side only (route handler, edge function, or background job — TBD)

