## Do not

- Call Supabase from `ui/` components — use repository → service → ViewModel
- Skip Zod validation on repository responses
- Expose internal UUIDs or provider IDs in UI models
- Hand-write DB types — use Supabase CLI
- Conflate **Account** (financial) with **User** (auth) or **Profile** (personal page)
